      "reviews": [
        {
          "reviewTitle": "Lightweight Liquid Foundation",
          "reviewText": "An exceptional foundation \u2014 flawless coverage, lightweight feel, and long-lasting finish. Use: Perfect for everyday wear or special occasions. Provides smooth, even coverage that conceals imperfections without looking heavy. Ease of Use: Applies easily with the built-in applicator. Blends beautifully with a brush, sponge, or fingertips. Quality: Excellent formula \u2014 breathable, non-cakey, and suitable for multiple skin types. Stays fresh all day without oxidation. Value for Money: Worth every penny \u2014 a small amount covers the entire face, so it lasts a long time. Functionality: Doubles as both foundation and concealer, reducing the need for extra products. Keeps skin looking natural and hydrated. Look: Delivers a smooth, radiant, and professional finish \u2014 perfect balance between matte and glow. \u2b50 Highly recommended! Great coverage, comfortable wear, and beautiful results that last all day.",
          "reviewDate": "Reviewed in the United States on October 26, 2025",
          "customer": "Yessica Blanco",
          "customerProfileUrl": "https://www.amazon.com/gp/profile/amzn1.account.AHDT42BJWLRUKMY4EQE2KHHPNIKQ",
          "customerStarsRating": 5,
          "productSpecs": {
            "color": "AR Neutral CN 52 - moderately fair, cool-neutral undertones"
          },
          "helpfulVotes": "3 people found this helpful"
        },
        {
          "reviewTitle": "Bought multiple times!",
          "reviewText": "Clinique foundation has become my go-to! The color match is spot-on and blends seamlessly, giving me a natural, even look without feeling cakey. It provides great coverage that lasts all day while still feeling lightweight and breathable. My skin feels soft, smooth, and never irritated\u2014perfect for sensitive skin. Definitely worth the price for how flawless and comfortable it makes my skin look!",
          "reviewDate": "Reviewed in the United States on November 6, 2025",
